### Buscar categoria por ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/categorias/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Atualizar categoria
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/categorias/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Vendas Online",
  "descricao": "Receitas de vendas online",
  "cor": "#007bff",
  "icone": "globe",
  "tipo_transacao": "entrada",
  "ativa": true
}

### Deletar categoria
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/categorias/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}